Tiny File Transport Server
version - 0.1 (2020 July 21)

Usage: ./cli [ip_address]	connect TFT Server

Command:
    close		- Secure shutdown of server and local client
    exit		- Exit local client
    quit		- Exit local client
    ls			- View server file list
    get <filename>	- Download a file from server to local
    put <filename>	- Upload a file from local to server    
